data.description: Welcome to this exquisitely renovated 1 bedroom, 1.5 bath condo located close to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Seamlessly blending modern sophistication with coastal charm, this residence offers a spacious open floor plan awash with natural sunlight, highlighting the exceptional finishes at every turn. Retreat to the primary suite, where luxury is paramount, complete with a sizable bedroom, and ample closet space, and an ensuite bath with premium fixtures and finishes. Beyond the walls of this haven, the 55+ community offers an array of amenities including a sparkling pool, sauna, fitness center, bocce ball, billiards, shuffle board, and more.  This is a unique opportunity that beckons--secure your piece of paradise today!
